{"tid":1670671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位好驚「俾中共有藉口話港獨」嘅，麻煩即刻同梁天琦割蓆，並停止嗌「光復香港，時代革命」","createTime":"2019-10-23T05:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T13:41:03.000Z","uid":131691,"like":140,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"44b31ebd2e3b4ecf0dda5dcc738a0875dec31c35","tid":1670671,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:25:15.000Z","msg":"「背後呢四隻字，好可惜因為打緊官司，唔講得」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pi8XSWp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpi8XSWp.jpg&h=0eaf2bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好激嬲中共呀！<br />\n咁做邊個最開心？<br />\n中計啦！中計啦！<br />\n伏呀！<br />\n邊個xyz就係鬼！<br />\n不割蓆，但係其實我割你蓆！<br />\n顧點自己先啦，btw 全世界 stand with Hong Kong! 點解？因為佢哋唔俾顧掂自己先，一定要顧香港。"},{"pid":"24e714793514bea1218b3033c0688a2b39eaf9a8","tid":1670671,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16db6b27c6db79496599be09a5689aea3b0d0b60","tid":1670671,"uid":199244,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:26:41.000Z","msg":"天琦：am I a joke to you?"},{"pid":"ad0f264c16d88e44fa2933f7bbeea80f96dd449e","tid":1670671,"uid":265192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=00ea4716\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=9402bb6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=a50f9467\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.